  "1874490": {
    "name": "魔药经济学：神秘的魔法药水商店",
    "steam_appid": 1874490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在叔叔突然离世后，身无分文的女巫希尔薇娅发现自己不得不承担起经营药水店的责任。她必须继承叔叔的遗志，让药水店继续运营下去。幸运的是，她并非孤军奋战。在一些新朋友的帮助下，希尔薇娅必须磨练自己的谈判技巧，战胜老谋深算的竞争对手，让自己的商店成为拉夫塔首屈一指的药水店。一切都取决于她能否掌握魔药经济学的奥妙！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874490/extras/a21fcfd982e7707b66fd6531ea5942cd.poster.avif?t=1750960791\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874490/extras/a21fcfd982e7707b66fd6531ea5942cd.webm?t=1750960791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874490/extras/a21fcfd982e7707b66fd6531ea5942cd.mp4?t=1750960791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>巧妙交易</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当每一分钱都至关重要时，谈判可能会变得剑拔弩张，但只要你善用手中的卡牌，就能轻松管理希尔薇娅的压力。与拉夫塔的冒险家和其他店主建立友谊，学习更高级的谈判技巧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成功配方</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择最佳的材料，即使是基础药水也能非同凡响，精心调制味道和香气来取悦最挑剔的顾客。但要小心——稍有不慎，结果可能就会非常糟糕！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>良友与劲敌</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拉夫塔，这个拥有世界上最强魔法的地方，汇聚了众多性格鲜明的RPG角色，每个人都渴望在冒险中获得优势。与他们结交并招募他们来提升自己调配药水的水平，但不要指望每个人都那么友善……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的商店你做主</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用可定制的装饰，让你的商店脱颖而出。风格点数可不是唯一的优势；恰到好处的商店装饰不仅可以提高药水价格，还能提升药水品质，好处多多！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874490/extras/99a770c53a30d1ddd44f95d2fdb2a0f8.poster.avif?t=1750960791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874490/extras/99a770c53a30d1ddd44f95d2fdb2a0f8.webm?t=1750960791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874490/extras/99a770c53a30d1ddd44f95d2fdb2a0f8.mp4?t=1750960791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
